1
00:00:01,480 --> 00:00:03,279
It's not for 
us to decide.

2
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:32,240
Watch that wire!

3
00:00:32,479 --> 00:00:33,679
Got it.

4
00:00:33,880 --> 00:00:35,320
Hey, stop!

5
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:36,159
Zanna!

6
00:00:36,159 --> 00:00:36,960
Stop!

7
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:40,439
Can you hear that?

8
00:00:42,039 --> 00:00:43,039
No...

9
00:00:51,399 --> 00:00:52,600
[distant church bell]

10
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:01,000
There is life in Libitina.

11
00:01:04,719 --> 00:01:05,719
Here.

12
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,840
[distant church bell]

13
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:19,079
[distant church bell]

14
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:24,959
[church bell]

15
00:01:34,159 --> 00:01:36,799
Everybody will be 
inside for Sunday Mass.

16
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:38,040
We need to warn them.

17
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:39,239
Matteo, wait.

18
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:42,079
I want to tell 
you something.

19
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:46,159
I don't remember how 
we met or what we did.

20
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:47,959
I just...

21
00:01:47,959 --> 00:01:49,959
... remember waking 
up with you.

22
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:52,159
... and

23
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:55,200
I'm really glad we did.

24
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:57,920
Same.

25
00:02:02,879 --> 00:02:04,879
<i>The souls of the just men</i>

26
00:02:06,319 --> 00:02:07,480
<i>and women</i>

27
00:02:08,319 --> 00:02:10,520
<i>must be cleansed by</i>

28
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:16,199
<i>temporary punishment.</i>

29
00:02:16,599 --> 00:02:20,719
<i>To be admitted into </i>
<i>the eternal country.</i>

30
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,560
[doors opening]

31
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:36,199
<i>Even the least pains in purgatory</i>

32
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:42,599
<i>are greater than what ever pain </i>
<i>is imaginable in the world.</i>

33
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:51,280
<i>The final purification</i>

34
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:55,280
<i>of the elect after death.</i>

35
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,560
Matteo...

36
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:03,759
Nonna?

37
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:05,520
Matteo, wait!

